{"id":364,"parent_id":351,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":364,"title":"1 Chronicles 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Chr.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","David fetches the ark from Kirjath-jearim—Uzza is slain by the Lord when he steadies the ark—The house of Obed-edom prospers because they care for the ark."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.1","order":"02.14.013.28379"},["b","1"],"And David consulted with the captains of thousands and hundreds,",["i","and"],"with every leader."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.2","order":"02.14.013.28380"},["b","2"],"And David said unto all the congregation of Israel, If",["i","it seem"],"good unto you, and",["i","that it be"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God, let us send abroad unto our brethren every where,",["i","that are"],"left in all the land of Israel, and with them",["i","also"],"to the priests and Levites",["i","which are"],"in their cities",["i","and"],"suburbs, that they may gather themselves unto us:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.3","order":"02.14.013.28381"},["b","3"],"And let us bring again the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"ark"],"of our God to us: for we inquired not at it in the days of Saul."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.4","order":"02.14.013.28382"},["b","4"],"And all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"congregation"],"said that they would do so: for the thing was right in the eyes of all the people."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.5","order":"02.14.013.28383"},["b","5"],"So David",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"gathered"],"all Israel together, from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Shihor"],"of Egypt even unto the entering of Hemath, to bring the ark of God from Kirjath-jearim."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.6","order":"02.14.013.28384"},["b","6"],"And David went up, and all Israel, to Baalah,",["i","that is,"],"to Kirjath-jearim, which",["i","belonged"],"to Judah, to bring up thence the ark of God the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that dwelleth",["i","between"],"the cherubims, whose name is called",["i","on it."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.7","order":"02.14.013.28385"},["b","7"],"And they carried the ark of God in a new cart out of the house of Abinadab: and Uzza and Ahio drave the cart."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.8","order":"02.14.013.28386"},["b","8"],"And David and all Israel played before God with all",["i","their"],"might, and with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"singing"],", and with harps, and with psalteries, and with timbrels, and with cymbals, and with trumpets."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.9","order":"02.14.013.28387"},["b","9"],"¶And when they came unto the threshingfloor of Chidon, Uzza put forth his hand to hold the ark; for the oxen stumbled."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.10","order":"02.14.013.28388"},["b","10"],"And the anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was kindled against Uzza, and he smote him, because he put his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"hand"],"to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"ark"],": and there he died before God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.11","order":"02.14.013.28389"},["b","11"],"And David was displeased, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had made a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"breach"],"upon Uzza: wherefore that place is called Perez-uzza to this day."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.12","order":"02.14.013.28390"},["b","12"],"And David was afraid of God that day, saying, How shall I bring the ark of God",["i","home"],"to me?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.13","order":"02.14.013.28391"},["b","13"],"So David brought not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"ark"],["i","home"],"to himself to the city of David, but carried it aside into the house of Obed-edom the Gittite."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.14","order":"02.14.013.28392"},["b","14"],"And the ark of God remained with the family of Obed-edom in his house three months. And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"blessed"],"the house of Obed-edom, and all that he had."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.3a","order":"02.14.013.28393"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/5.1.1-12"},"1 Sam. 5:1 (1–12)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ark-of-the-covenant"},"TG Ark of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.4a","order":"02.14.013.28395"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/26.2"},"D&C 26:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.5a","order":"02.14.013.28397"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.1"},"2 Sam. 6:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.5b","order":"02.14.013.28399"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/23.3"},"Isa. 23:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.8a","order":"02.14.013.28401"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.12"},"D&C 25:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.10a","order":"02.14.013.28403"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/4.15"},"Num. 4:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.10b","order":"02.14.013.28405"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/15.2"},"1 Chr. 15:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.8"},"D&C 85:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.11a","order":"02.14.013.28407"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/15.13"},"1 Chr. 15:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.13a","order":"02.14.013.28409"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.2.1-11"},"2 Sam. 6:2 (1–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.14a","order":"02.14.013.28411"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/26.5.4-5"},"1 Chr. 26:5 (4–5)"],"."]]}
